{"tid":924537,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又玩房地產？科學園正興建宿舍，提供500多個宿位","createTime":"2018-12-02T07:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T10:44:42.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"50802d4aa2abc0e7f5fad7ce48e3da0165845fb5","tid":924537,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:32:28.000Z","msg":"政府早前公布撥款100億港元予科學園，外界關注科學園如何分配這筆巨款。香港科技園公司行政總裁黃克強今早(2日)在電台節目表示，款項主要用於加強支援初創企業，及為園內企業提供租金支援以協助尋找投資者，並正研究設立共用實驗室，希望可以扶植出1000間初創企業。他指，科技園亦會向當局爭取簡化初創企業研發資金申請程序，縮短申請時間。<br />\n<br />\n黃表示，香港開始形成創科氣氛，過往很多有能力的人才未有積極投身研發，亦欠缺機會，現時有政策支持，加上科學園作為孵化平台，相信有一定鼓勵作用。他補充，科學園正興建宿舍，提供500多個宿位，希望為來港的科研人才解決居住成本太高的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181202/bkn-20181202102354298-1202_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181202%2Fbkn-20181202102354298-1202_00822_001.html&d=ANChfUt99FUJmRYkrR0xNnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=07e26296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181202/bkn-20181202102354298-1202_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1761b0d8418b6c88513086fe095f0717da593d66","tid":924537,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:32:55.000Z","msg":"改名叫 地產園好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80279894f3f5aa2c3f8bad8dd2b2b06c7f475f51","tid":924537,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:36:34.000Z","msg":"科技園係樓盤名黎"},{"pid":"f77ab1f26262bfd92d0ed5ee2f387219cb515ed5","tid":924537,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1761b0d8418b6c88513086fe095f0717da593d66","tid":924537,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:32:55.000Z","msg":"改名叫 地產園好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />